---
title: Panko-Topped Double Salmon with Broccoli, Buttery Green Pea Rice and Lemony Mayo
description: Crunchy, golden breadcrumbs make this easy baked salmon a fast family favourite! Our DIY lemony mayo is great dolloped onto the salmon and served as a dipper for broccoli.
